svg.title: UML 2.5
svg.desc: A template for all diagrams of UML 2.5 and earlier versions. For help and latest version of the template please visit http://softwarestencils.com. Template version: 27. December 2013. Known issues: The "hand-drawn" themes and the "shady" theme may have "desctructive" effect on some shapes.
